"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"The current game economy system is a planned economy. Game companies sell equipment and currencies to players, just like issuing food and meat tickets. Players can only use specific tickets to buy specific things and achieve specific functions. Tickets do not have currency attributes. Players cannot legally trade tickets, and it is even more impossible for players to sell tickets to game companies. Players can only sell their own labor, that is, consume time or pay in the game. \\n\\nImagine what happens when this economic model becomes a market economy? Players' enthusiasm will inevitably be mobilized. China's decades of development have profoundly proven this point. The wealth acquired by game companies will definitely increase so much that it will exceed Amazon, Apple, and Google, and eventually a company with a market value over 10 trillion will be born.\",\"timestamp\":1641143849,\"title\":\"Capsule（13.6.2021）Game Economy System\"},\"digest\":\"dRCk2T1-zLy3cL6tGkq20tPev19a7vbS1XGDyxmqm0k\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xE828f8bE1a3CB994133936fB4D9A708a7D192462\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"cWndKezD0ZiMgnYOqspWtyALlI_KYDziYOZaOerHeCY\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"Kf7VHolS02uUcQvJnvpP7ci_9wxCwvj1KsxIdy1wyS4\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"TzKI52ikMe2QC6-ExCcWYNy8VcMHyJJlK_OYPktasCr4N1vviPGx1LSvlZnlXsPexNuPUeBsFLvwAH4DzcCbKQ\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x24845bd906a3dcd3a6a2c8def0e1867a94aa37e04d35018a13b94099ae5be24d4b1abdd27984d765963fd65aa852fe7e1dc6d3934335a6e14328e5bca1565db21b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"cWndKezD0ZiMgnYOqspWtyALlI_KYDziYOZaOerHeCY\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"Kf7VHolS02uUcQvJnvpP7ci_9wxCwvj1KsxIdy1wyS4\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nf